      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a strong start, but we need to make it even more specific so people realize the danger is real and imminent. In my vision, I saw how they use these international banking systems and \"green\" policies to basically bankrupt independent families and force everyone into their digital control systems. Can we add a section about how these specific globalist agendas are designed to strip away our national identities and leave us with no choice but to obey their central authority?",
